    AtlasNode { kind: "C", id: "PIXIE-008-airgenome-6axis-recap", raw: "@C PIXIE-008-airgenome-6axis-recap = airgenome long-topic restates \"6-axis hexagon projection ŌĆö vital signs live on one shape\" with axes (CPU/RAM/Swap/Net/Disk/GPU) ŌĆö this IS the genuine n=6 anchor in the pixie corpus, but it is a RECAP of airgenome, not pixie's own structure :: pixie/worker/src/topics.js L131-L138 [7]\n  => recap-of-anchor (n=6 lives in airgenome, pixie quotes it)\n  => recap-of-anchor (n=6 lives in airgenome, pixie quotes it)", source_file: "atlas.append.pixie-gohive-2026-04-27.n6", source_line: 79 },
