    AtlasNode { kind: "C", id: "SEDI-AR2-COMBINED-SIG-FISHER", raw: "@C SEDI-AR2-COMBINED-SIG-FISHER = Findings 1+2+3 (QCD ladder 3.80Žā + Higgs decay 3.89Žā + quark-lepton bridge 3.40Žā) ŌåÆ Fisher combined p = 4.16e-10, Fisher Žā = 6.14, Stouffer Žā = 6.40 ; aggressive 7-finding combination yields 7.23Žā Fisher / 7.55Žā Stouffer :: meta-statistics [10*PROBE_RUN]\n  => \"Recommended combination = 6.14Žā Fisher (most defensible) per source.\"\n  => \"Recommended combination = 6.14Žā Fisher (most defensible) per source.\"\n  => \"PRESERVED CAVEAT (not in source): the ŽāŽå=nŽä identity is the COMMON CAUSE of all three p-values; a Bayesian model with this prior would deflate the Fisher result substantially.\"\n  => \"PRESERVED CAVEAT (not in source): the ŽāŽå=nŽä identity is the COMMON CAUSE of all three p-values; a Bayesian model with this prior would deflate the Fisher result substantially.\"\n// ŌöĆŌöĆ 3. Cross-domain triangular constant matrix ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ", source_file: "atlas.append.sedi-archive-deep-batch-2-2026-04-27.n6", source_line: 93 },
